data.description: This home is nestled down under mature trees and shrubs creating just the right mix of privacy for this cozy ranch styled home. Custom loft area in living room as well as a wood burning Stove. Enclosed back porch with sliding glass doors and a walk out basement plus a fenced in back yard and so much more!
